reviewText: The most original,  funny and sentimental programs ever!!
Be sure to look closely at the package.  I knew it was "too good to be true".  Only 3 episodes on that DVD.  What is up with that?  "Slight of hand", I suppose.  Very disappointing.

Of course, this old series, that I watched along time ago. I seat and watched them, with my grandkids and my (one) great-grandson. Every day situations,and how they were deal with,and family life and the bond.
